table_description: This table contains metadata about the analysis results collections available in IDC. Each row corresponds to an analysis results collection, and contains attributes such as the collection name, types of cancer represented, number of subjects, and pointers to the resources to learn more about the content of the collection

columns.name: analysis_result_id
columns.description: unique identifier of the analysis results collection

columns.name: analysis_result_title
columns.description: name of the analysis results collection

columns.name: source_DOI
columns.description: Digital Object Identifier (DOI) of the analysis results collection

columns.name: source_url
columns.description: URL for the location of additional information about the analysis results collection

columns.name: Subjects
columns.description: number of subjects analyzed in the analysis results collection

columns.name: Collections
columns.description: collections analyzed in the analysis results collection

columns.name: Modalities
columns.description: modalities corresponding to the analysis artifacts included in the analysis results collection

columns.name: Updated
columns.description: timestamp of the last update to the analysis results collection

columns.name: license_url
columns.description: license URL for the analysis results collection

columns.name: license_long_name
columns.description: license name for the analysis results collection

columns.name: license_short_name
columns.description: short name for the license of the analysis results collection

columns.name: Description
columns.description: detailed description of the analysis results collection

columns.name: Citation
columns.description: citation for the analysis results collection that should be used for acknowledgment
